[{"href":"https://navajowhite-turkey-121983.hostingersite.com/wp-json/wc/v3/products"}],"self":[{"href":"https://navajowhite-turkey-121983.hostingersite.com/wp-json/wc/v3/products/4328","targetHints":"[Object]"}]},"attributes":[],"average_rating":"0.00","backordered":false,"backorders":"no","backorders_allowed":false,"brands":[],"button_text":"","catalog_visibility":"visible","categories":[{"id":185,"name":"ROUTINE ULTRASOUND","slug":"routine-ultrasound"}],"cross_sell_ids":[],"date_created":"2026-03-31T09:51:28","date_created_gmt":"2026-03-31T09:51:28","date_modified":"2026-04-04T07:06:58","date_modified_gmt":"2026-04-04T07:06:58","date_on_sale_from":null,"date_on_sale_from_gmt":null,"date_on_sale_to":null,"date_on_sale_to_gmt":null,"default_attributes":[],"description":"<p>Whole abdomen ultrasound  is like a full-body check for your insides. It's used for:<br />\n- Liver health: Detecting issues like fatty liver, cysts, or tumors<br />\n- Gallbladder check: Looking for stones or inflammation<br />\n- Kidney assessment: Checking for stones, cysts, or size issues<br />\n- Spleen size: Detecting enlargement or abnormalities<br />\n- Pancreas check: Looking for inflammation or tumors<br />\n- Abdominal fluid: Detecting free fluid or ascites</p>\n<p>It's often done for abdominal pain, abnormal reports, or routine check-ups.</p>\n<p>Let's get detailed . A whole abdomen ultrasound is a comprehensive scan covering major organs. Here are its key uses:<br />\n- Liver assessment: Detecting cirrhosis, tumors, or fatty changes<br />\n- Gallbladder evaluation: Identifying stones, inflammation, or polyps<br />\n- Kidney check: Looking for stones, cysts, tumors, or size abnormalities<br />\n- Spleen examination: Checking size and detecting issues<br />\n- Pancreas inspection: Detecting pancreatitis or tumors<br />\n- Abdominal aorta check: Looking for aneurysms or blockages<br />\n- Fluid detection: Identifying ascites or free fluid in the abdomen</p>\n<p>It's super useful for investigating abdominal pain, abnormal reports, or pre-surgical checks.</p>\n<p><strong>PREPERATION</strong></p>\n<p>-Minimum three hours fasting required preferably overnight.</p>\n<p><strong>APPOINTMENT REQUIRED</strong></p>\n","dimensions":{"height":"","length":"","width":""},"download_expiry":-1,"download_limit":-1,"downloadable":false,"downloads":[],"external_url":"","featured":true,"global_unique_id":"","grouped_products":[],"has_options":false,"id":4328,"images":[],"low_stock_amount":null,"manage_stock":false,"menu_order":0,"meta_data":[],"name":"ULTRASOUND WHOLE ABDOMEN  W/A","on_sale":false,"parent_id":0,"permalink":"https://navajowhite-turkey-121983.hostingersite.com/product/ultrasound-whole-abdomen/","post_password":"","price":"2300","price_html":"<span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\"><bdi><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#8377;</span>2,300.00</bdi></span>","purchasable":true,"purchase_note":"","rating_count":0,"regular_price":"2300","related_ids":[4326,4378,4388,4332,4389],"reviews_allowed":true,"sale_price":"","shipping_class":"","shipping_class_id":0,"shipping_required":true,"shipping_taxable":true,"short_description":"<p>Whole abdomen ultrasound  is like a full-body check for your insides. It&#8217;s used for:<br />\n&#8211; Liver health: Detecting issues like fatty liver, cysts, or tumors<br />\n&#8211; Gallbladder check: Looking for stones or inflammation<br />\n&#8211; Kidney assessment: Checking for stones, cysts, or size issues<br />\n&#8211; Spleen size: Detecting enlargement or abnormalities<br />\n&#8211; Pancreas check: Looking for inflammation or tumors<br />\n&#8211; Abdominal fluid: Detecting free fluid or ascites</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s often done for abdominal pain, abnormal reports, or routine check-ups.</p>\n<p><strong>PREPERATION</strong></p>\n<p>-Minimum three hours fasting required preferably overnight.</p>\n<p><strong>APPOINTMENT REQUIRED</strong></p>\n","sku":"","slug":"ultrasound-whole-abdomen","sold_individual